lead_paragraph: The plane that crashed in Colombia killing 71 people was owned by a Venezuelan businessman and one-time leftist politician and run by a tiny Bolivian company specializing in transporting soccer teams.

headline.print_headline: Crashed Plane Owned by Venezuelan, Operated by Tiny Bolivian Airline
